  <brief_title>Comparison of Reversal of Neuromuscular Blockade With Sugammadex Versus Neostigmine Plus Glycopyrolate in Patients Undergoing Burn Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Reversal of Neuromuscular Blockade With Sugammadex Versus Neostigmine Plus Glycopyrolate in Patients Undergoing Burn Surgery</official_title>
