  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to learn if there is a difference in recovery time when using
      sugammadex versus neostigmine. The researchers also hope to add further knowledge and data to
      the safety of using sugammadex in burn patients who are hypermetabolic.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
